A key-ready exclusive residential project with new apartments and penthouses with 2 and 3 bedrooms with contemporary Mediterranean styling located at the heart of the famous San Roque Club resort.&#13;
&#13;
The plot occupies a privileged position above the famous “Old Course” golf course which literally surrounds it. It is an emerald green oasis, with views predominantly over the sea, the clubhouse and of the intense colour of the greens.&#13;
&#13;
THE DEVELOPMENT&#13;
This residential project has 80 apartments in 10 three storey buildings, spread over three phases that surround the 3 communal pools.&#13;
&#13;
